{"tid":1727074,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[士氣post] 場抗爭行唔行到落去，最重要唔係有冇rb，而係有冇人呀！！！","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:46:01.000Z","uid":161430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0aee888afa0305170d9d14569f6bccade7cd5d15","tid":1727074,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"手足，roadblock呢d野，<br />\n冇左可以再整，冇左亦唔代表d乜。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，六月開始到之後好長時間，<br />\n本來都冇周街路障添，<br />\n當時既行動，仲要星期六日先有大遊行添，<br />\n咁場抗爭咪又係未停過，冇轉弱過，<br />\n咪又係一路走來到宜家。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者試過百萬人和理非遊行，<br />\n又試過陣地，試過攻入立法會、圍警總，<br />\n又試過be water流水式，整rb，三罷，<br />\n總之乜都試過，抗爭都係完全唔會停。<br />\n<br />\n點解可以咁？<br />\n係因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人丫嘛<br />\n總之有人出，就乜都可以有，<br />\n冇左都可以再有，有乜好驚？有乜需要介懷？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n邊種方法唔work，只要有人出，<br />\n自然會轉化有第二種work既方法，<br />\n只要個個肯企出黎，場抗爭又點會完？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔該香港人，今日、今星期開始，<br />\n跟住個日程表，開始新一輪反抗啦，<br />\n要出黎，要多人呀<br />\n多人就係最重要</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3ff6fcf50f4a7fc866a9fa746e97aa2a05918c55","tid":1727074,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b41435830fa9645b373b8741f714a6410a1a8a","tid":1727074,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5f3f28302e3de9b4fafc0c5265102a981a99de","tid":1727074,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef0e5ab877f4afd82da1a98500482c46d3500c7","tid":1727074,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f